---
Source:
  URL: "http://pkrishnan.net/satyam-bruyat-priyam-\
    bruyat-na-bruyat-satyam-apriyam/"
  Locus:
    Date: 24 March 2018
  Source:
    Title: Manusmriti
---
Speak truth in such a way that it should be pleasing to others. Never speak
truth, which is unpleasant to others. Never speak untruth, which might be
pleasant. This is the path of eternal morality, sanatana dharma.
